sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Виконавець/Admin
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant ApiService
    participant API as FastAPI task endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant TG as Telegram Bot API
    participant FCM as Firebase Cloud Messaging

    User->>App: Завершує задачу
    App->>ApiService: completeTask(taskId)
    ApiService->>API: POST /tasks/{task_id}/complete
    API->>DB: load Task
    API->>DB: set status=done, completed_by=current_user.id
    API->>DB: load assignments and creator
    loop виконавці та автор
        alt має telegram_id
            API->>TG: send completion message
        end
        alt має fcm_token
            API->>FCM: send task_completed push
        end
    end
    API-->>ApiService: status done

    actor Admin as Admin/Superadmin
    Admin->>App: Повертає задачу в роботу
    App->>ApiService: reopenTask(taskId)
    ApiService->>API: POST /tasks/{task_id}/reopen
    API->>DB: check role and load task
    API->>DB: set status=active, completed_by=null
    loop виконавці
        API->>TG: send reopened task message
        API->>FCM: send reopen push
    end
    API-->>ApiService: status active
